 fuse4bsd [kfreebsd-any],
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 libntfs-3g851,
 ntfsprogs (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: read/write NTFS driver for FUSE
 NTFS-3G uses FUSE (Filesystem in Userspace) to provide support for the NTFS
 filesystem used by Microsoft Windows.

